Can you explain why the command `ST sendcurrency "*" '[{"address":"mike@","convertto":"gold","preconvert":1,"amount":100}]'` will immediately convert my VRSCTEST to GOLD?

The command `ST sendcurrency "*" '[{"address":"mike@","convertto":"gold","preconvert":1,"amount":100}]'` does not immediately convert your VRSCTEST to GOLD. Instead, it parks your conversion until the GOLD token launches. Once the token launches, you will either find 0.975 GOLD in your wallet, or you will have your VRSCTEST back.
